Aina stood, waiting while the other amazon came to her side. &quot;Palus, our priestess will now also welcome our princess.&quot; Aina bit her lip. She could never remember the words to say during welcoming ceremonies. The Amazons clapped as Xerena was initiated as princess. The Queen scowled politely, even though she scowled on the inside. It was one thing having to accept Xerena as a Sister, but to have to give her the right of caste too?! Palus' smile over Xerena's head was greeted with a wink from the Queen, a wink that didn't go unnoticed by the rest of the council. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6A74B4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=kiraeuryleia>Kira Euryleia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#FFFF00>(7/6/01 12:56:43 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: First Order Of Business....</span><hr size=1> *Later on, Xerena sat in the hut she was given. There she held her sword, looking it over with wonder and sadness.<br>
  'My mother's sword as well as her name&quot;Xerena&quot;...now mine. One a great Amazon Queen....  now dead like all the rest. <br>
    Can i live up to her title? I didnt expect any one to welcome me into this tribe,let alone allow me to become princess. <br>
    But i saw there stares... their thoughts of if they were wrong to give em this right of caste.<br>
Were they? <br>
   Just like everyone else I will have to prove myself.Like i always do. But i wonder if i can start over here... start fresh.<br>
It may be a new begining, a second chance, but does it mean<br>
I can escape my past or shall it all repeat and i will have to leave again...?' Xerena's thoughts could not be finish when an Amazon knocked at her door.<br>
&quot;Come in.&quot;<br>
 &quot;Xerena... Queen Aina and the High Council would like to have a word with you.&quot;<br>
&quot;I'll be right there.&quot; *Xerena arose from hebed and sheathed her sword. And quickly followed the Amazon to the High Council*<br>
